 in freight is dead, why is it still running the yard?</h3></a><p class="blog-card__excerpt" data-v-415a7f80>Cargo fraud has made the yard the supply chain&#39;s most exposed point, yet yard security and yard management have always been treated as separate problems bought from separate vendors. Terminal&#39;s argument: AI-native development has collapsed that tradeoff, making it possible for the first time to converge both into one system at the gate, where custody actually changes and the decision to lift the arm still matters</p><!----></div></div></div><div class="blog-card featured-blog-posts__item" data-v-aad9c107 data-v-415a7f80><div class="blog-card__wrapper" data-v-415a7f80><div class="blog-card__image-wrapper" data-v-415a7f80><a href="/all-resources/gate-entry-computer-vision" class="" aria-label="Read more about {{ story.content.title }}" data-v-415a7f80><img onerror="this.setAttribute(&#39;data-error&#39;, 1)" width="400" height="400" alt="Gate Entry - Computer Vision " data-nuxt-img srcset="/storyblok/f/337048/2892x1594/059d3122cb/y.webp 1x, /storyblok/f/337048/2892x1594/059d3122cb/y.webp 2x" class="blog-card__image" src="/storyblok/f/337048/2892x1594/059d3122cb/y.webp" data-v-415a7f80><button class="blog-card__button button label-4 blog-card__button" style="--hover-bg:rgba(5, 36, 36, 1);--hover-color:rgba(171, 255, 2, 1);--base-color:white;" data-v-415a7f80 data-v-d8fa3fef><span class="link-active" data-v-d8fa3fef><!--[-->Watch Now<!--]--></span></button></a></div><div class="blog-card__content" data-v-415a7f80><p class="blog-card__category" data-v-415a7f80>video</p><a href="/all-resources/gate-entry-computer-vision" class="" aria-label="Read more about {{ story.content.title }}" data-v-415a7f80><h3 class="blog-card__title" data-v-415a7f80>Gate Entry - Computer Vision </h3></a><p class="blog-card__excerpt" data-v-415a7f80>Gate Entry - Computer Vision </p><!----></div></div></div><div class="blog-card featured-blog-posts__item" data-v-aad9c107 data-v-415a7f80><div class="blog-card__wrapper" data-v-415a7f80><div class="blog-card__image-wrapper" data-v-415a7f80><a href="/all-resources/gate-automation-systems-boost-security-efficiency-today" class="" aria-label="Read more about {{ story.content.title }}" data-v-415a7f80><img onerror="this.setAttribute(&#39;data-error&#39;, 1)" width="400" height="400" alt="Gate Automation Systems: Boost Security &amp; Efficiency Today" data-nuxt-img srcset="/storyblok/f/337048/1856x1192/e0e9c40a04/u.webp 1x, /storyblok/f/337048/1856x1192/e0e9c40a04/u.webp 2x" class="blog-card__image" src="/storyblok/f/337048/1856x1192/e0e9c40a04/u.webp" data-v-415a7f80><button class="blog-card__button button label-4 blog-card__button" style="--hover-bg:rgba(5, 36, 36, 1);--hover-color:rgba(171, 255, 2, 1);--base-color:white;" data-v-415a7f80 data-v-d8fa3fef><span class="link-active" data-v-d8fa3fef><!--[-->Read More<!--]--></span></button></a></div><div class="blog-card__content" data-v-415a7f80><p class="blog-card__category" data-v-415a7f80>blog</p><a href="/all-resources/gate-automation-systems-boost-security-efficiency-today" class="" aria-label="Read more about {{ story.content.title }}" data-v-415a7f80><h3 class="blog-card__title" data-v-415a7f80>Gate Automation Systems: Boost Security &amp; Efficiency Today</h3></a><p class="blog-card__excerpt" data-v-415a7f80>A gate automation system is a technology that turns traditional manual entry points into smart, self-operating access controls. It combines hardware like automated barriers, sensors, and cameras with advanced software to manage vehicle and personnel entry without the need for human involvement.</p><!----></div></div></div><!--]--></div></section><!--]--></div><div class="footer__height-holder --static" data-v-0da6245d><div class="--static overlay-sticky__wrapper" data-v-0da6245d></div><div class="--static footer__wrapper" data-v-0da6245d><div class="svg-mask" data-v-0da6245d style="--d27fb6da:url(#clip-v-0-0-0-0);--b18bdda2:url(#mask-v-0-0